{"tid":607363,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【點解嘅？】搭新幹線笠住膠袋 日本AV女優︰我驚影響人哋","createTime":"2018-03-27T08:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T00:45:05.000Z","uid":26658,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"786a9acdd4496c0aabb60d24921f1da39673e7a9","tid":607363,"uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"出名饞嘴的日本AV女優桃乃木香奈不時在網上分享美食照，她近日上載多張乘搭新幹線時照片卻「造型奇特」︰她用一個大膠袋罩住頭部至肩部，原來是她在車上大啖豬肉包，為減低食物濃郁香氣對其他乘客的影響，因此就這樣做了。<br />\n<br />\n桃乃木香奈吃的是在大阪大受歡迎的豬肉包，她知道肉包的香氣太誘人，為其他乘客設想決定用膠袋罩著自己，躲在「保護罩」之下才進食，減少香氣飄散。照片見她一手拿著包裝盒，一手將包往口裡送，吃得津津有味。她在Twitter寫道：「在新幹線內能不能吃肉包一直有爭議，由於我實在忍不住，請原諒我」。<br />\n她後來再出帖文寫道：「這比我想像的更尷尬，由於膠袋是透明的，車掌看到我時也大笑。」並附上一張在膠袋內邊拿包邊掩嘴笑的可愛照片。網民笑稱她為了吃可以奇招盡出，也有人大讚她可愛又貼心。<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》/Twitter  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/165150_b8add983e1a98f35f3defc8679566523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F165150_b8add983e1a98f35f3defc8679566523.jpg&h=e82fe9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/165150_268ad1e69522f9290ec18c4908541e00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F165150_268ad1e69522f9290ec18c4908541e00.jpg&h=77d05f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/165151_18027e4f9059e41ca56ec3f90dd0a5b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F165151_18027e4f9059e41ca56ec3f90dd0a5b0.jpg&h=cd69e538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/165152_00be2c84c49a8d3414371123ea8e4dfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F165152_00be2c84c49a8d3414371123ea8e4dfa.jpg&h=6012d578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/165152_86f959b4f3a4ab903e67232ef34d2317.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F165152_86f959b4f3a4ab903e67232ef34d2317.jpg&h=c5e67081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180326/57992070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F57992070&d=kVF0zWoN3lybMO8wK4pXWhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=53c612cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F57992070&h=331421da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180326/57992070</a>"},{"pid":"4eb0804bd81712d4c0e19782847370f2706ad5b9","tid":607363,"uid":43870,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"又有新av主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498713adecac2c9ba88bcb383c20434aa2014b3d","tid":607363,"uid":1049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"桃奶木勁好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bf0088d2b0cee059b6360bcbd1f37ce64d211a","tid":607363,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"日本女仔啲私服look好撚正"},{"pid":"7ca4bd59100a9b00003e02e248c1ae3a42361fc9","tid":607363,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eab8577bc91eddd0b91973957a2efa9c114c9ba","tid":607363,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"個包真係堅撚正㗎<br />\n<br />\n佢果兩個我都想試下"},{"pid":"ef7cd5e1bb4a1a5ec5bc62d018a1dee843a522ab","tid":607363,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"依隻臭雞算有自知之明<br />\n驚自己拍av惹返黎既性病透過座位傳染比一般人"},{"pid":"afe2f232f2c170c42fccdb9000386e6257c882fc","tid":607363,"uid":26658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T20:50:29.000Z","msg":"好想同佢係個大膠袋入面一齊做愛，膠袋入面係哂我同佢d汗水，熱帶夜，哥浸淫味，諗起都扯旗！"},{"pid":"5f134339c9e434a48b3a0747afabd9b0cda2d615","tid":607363,"uid":50310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T21:07:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老姆！講起就把火<br />\n搭巴士啲廢老永遠照開電話睇戲、打機<br />\n從不用耳機<br />\n驚死其他人唔知道佢睇緊乜！<br />\n<br />\n唔想煩擾別人，呢樣係日本文化的美德<br />\n可惜香港極多欠奉<br />\n以為用耳機係自閉仔<br />\n要嘈到人至安樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3473dfadc27960fe5dae688d3e47dd0806eaa71c","tid":607363,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T21:49:07.000Z","msg":"桃奶木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f625e046c8ff50d3e01a7cda0d59e121e9ef7bc3","tid":607363,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb0804bd81712d4c0e19782847370f2706ad5b9","tid":607363,"uid":43870,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"又有新av主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T23:57:55.000Z","msg":"笠著個膠袋黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55c7b734039d0bb46ff9be7dce5c1b30cf634a3",